might put in the middle, right?

00:06:24.821 --> 00:06:25.320
Somewhere.

00:06:25.320 --> 00:06:26.750
Maybe even put
students in the middle

00:06:26.750 --> 00:06:28.083
and structures in the next ring.

00:06:28.083 --> 00:06:32.670
But this triangle is so key
to everything that we do.

00:06:32.670 --> 00:06:35.050
And then for us
at the Ed school,

00:06:35.050 --> 00:06:36.870
when we think
about this, we have

00:06:36.870 --> 00:06:38.840
this larger external
environment,

00:06:38.840 --> 00:06:41.539
which is comprised
of all these rings.

00:06:41.539 --> 00:06:43.830
But what's interesting at
the Ed school that's going on

00:06:43.830 --> 00:06:46.726
that we really should echo--

00:06:46.726 --> 00:06:47.225
I'm sorry.

00:06:47.225 --> 00:06:48.720
What's going on
in the environment

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:51.030
that we need to echo
at the Ed school is

00:06:51.030 --> 00:06:55.440
this real shift towards
thinking about how to recreate

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:59.550
an environment here in which
students are not just kind

00:06:59.550 --> 00:07:02.040
of engaging in rote memorization
and so forth, but really

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:03.640
engaging in what we call--

00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:05.740
some of the faculty
called deeper learning

00:07:05.740 --> 00:07:08.790
and complex cognitive
thinking skills

00:07:08.790 --> 00:07:10.750
and project-based
learning and all of those

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:14.640
that we're actually
enabling our own students

00:07:14.640 --> 00:07:17.700
to go out and enact and
be professionals, right?

00:07:17.700 --> 00:07:20.760
But then we need to
do the same thing.

00:07:20.760 --> 00:07:21.570
Right?

00:07:21.570 --> 00:07:24.040
So we can't sit and
lecture and so forth.

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:26.235
It's a lot more than
flipped classrooms.

00:07:26.235 --> 00:07:28.774
I mean, we've gotten rid
of courses, in some cases.

00:07:28.774 --> 00:07:29.940
Some cases, we have modules.

00:07:29.940 --> 00:07:31.350
Some cases, we have labs.

00:07:31.350 --> 00:07:36.270
Some cases, we are actually
consulting to the Children's

00:07:36.270 --> 00:07:37.470
Defense Fund and so forth.

00:07:37.470 --> 00:07:40.760
And we're doing-- we're
trying to really recreate

00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:44.640
the environment that we
aspire for our students

00:07:44.640 --> 00:07:45.950
when they leave the Ed school.

00:07:45.950 --> 00:07:48.620
