or PowerPoint,

00:07:57.760 --> 00:08:00.450
et cetera, some a little
bit of flipped classroom,

00:08:00.450 --> 00:08:04.500
but not that much to a
completely different model.

00:08:04.500 --> 00:08:05.955
How do we evaluate that?

00:08:05.955 --> 00:08:07.810
How do we teach--

00:08:07.810 --> 00:08:12.324
how do we teach our faculty
how to change in that way?

00:08:12.324 --> 00:08:13.920
How do we select faculty?

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.692
That's our biggest
issue right now.

00:08:15.692 --> 00:08:17.400
We look at their course
evals, but that's

00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:19.733
nothing-- has nothing to do
with what we want them to do

00:08:19.733 --> 00:08:21.120
once they get to the Ed school.

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:22.930
